    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Human settlements located on hills; hill settlements can be prehistoric and defensive in origin, or contemporary settlements built on higher ground. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
